This paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category as it proposes a new algorithm for feature selection in reinforcement learning. It may also be relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category as it deals with decision-making processes. Additionally, it involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY) as it deals with optimizing the sample complexity of a Factored Markov Decision Process.
